  <function id="cybozu::signal_setup" name="signal_setup">
    <brief>Block signals and create <ref ref="cybozu::signal_reader#cybozu::signal_reader">cybozu::signal_reader</ref> for blocked signals.</brief>
    <doc>This function blocks given signals and creates a <ref ref="cybozu::signal_reader#cybozu::signal_reader">cybozu::signal_reader</ref>
prepared to read blocked signals.  In addition, this configures
